March 13, 1967.

' No. —.

Lee, Corrections Commissioner, et al. v. Washington et al. MacDonald Gallion, Attorney General of Alabama, Gordon Madison, Assistant Attorney General, and Nicholas S. Haré, Special Assistant Attorney . General, for applicants. Charles Morgan and Orzell Bill-ingsley, Jr., in opposition.

D. C. M. D. Ala.. Application for . a stay presented to Mr. Justice Black, and by him referred to the Court, granted pending final disposition of , the . appeal • by this Court, provided the jurisdictional statement is 'filed and case docketed in this Court within 20 days from this date.
